        {
          "type": "incorrect_translation",
          "description": "The Lao translation 'ສະແດງປະຫວັດສະບັບ' translates to 'Show version history' but 'ສະບັບ' (version/edition) is used as a noun without a clear connection to 'history' in a way that sounds natural for a UI label. More importantly, 'ປະຫວັດສະບັບ' is grammatically awkward; it should be 'ປະຫວັດການໃຊ້ງານແຕ່ລະສະບັບ' or 'ປະຫວັດຂອງເວີຊັນ' to clearly mean 'version history'. However, the most critical error is that 'ສະບັບ' alone doesn't convey the concept of 'history of versions' effectively in this context.",
